<HL>
   Former Executives
   Of Cineplex Unit
   Name Firm in Suit
   ----
   By Suzanne McGee
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/05/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B6
</SO>
